	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Shiru wrote a library called Famitone which supports a limited subset of Famitracker (and sound effects).
<br />
<br /><a href="http://shiru.untergrund.net/code.shtml" class="postlink">http://shiru.untergrund.net/code.shtml</a>
<br />
<br />
<br />Famitracker's driver itself isn't really designed to be used with anything else. I don't think CPU usage is <em>too</em> bad, but the driver size and RAM usage are a bit prohibitive. It's okay for a demo.[/url]

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


